#: admin/views/gvl.php:21
msgid ""
"The Global Vendor List is published by IAB Europe and contains all "
"registered ad-tech vendors with their declared purposes and legal bases. "
"Select the vendors you work with to include them in the TCF consent flow."
msgstr ""
"La Global Vendor List (GVL) è gestita da IAB Europe e contiene tutti i "
"fornitori ad-tech registrati. Viene aggiornata automaticamente ogni "
"settimana."

